  "detailed_description": "<h1>联系我们：</h1><p>欢迎关注我们了解《未命名穿越记录》的最新进展：<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>官方微博：@GameraGame<br></li><li>官方QQ群：<strong>1003214338</strong></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>一次突入其来的穿越<br>一个即将毁灭的世界<br>一段无法割舍的感情<br>一场难以忘怀的冒险</strong><br><br>《未命名穿越记录》是一款融合了多种元素的复古风游戏——<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548680/extras/a5b4c559fc541627dcdc275ae3d65535.poster.avif?t=1745568966\" width=630 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548680/extras/a5b4c559fc541627dcdc275ae3d65535.webm?t=1745568966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548680/extras/a5b4c559fc541627dcdc275ae3d65535.mp4?t=1745568966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>丰富且充满分支的剧本。<br>你所决定的不仅是剧情，更有无法预料的暗中影响。<br><br><strong>近十个不同的结局，只有了解一切方能得知故事的真相</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548680/extras/5d242f1c95833897ceafbd54d524ce19.poster.avif?t=1745568966\" width=630 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548680/extras/5d242f1c95833897ceafbd54d524ce19.webm?t=1745568966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548680/extras/5d242f1c95833897ceafbd54d524ce19.mp4?t=1745568966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>精细多彩的角色特性以及不同的技能组合</li></ul>从同伴与敌人身上学习魔法与技能知识纳为己用。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>丰富的装备系统</li></ul>无论是地城探险、商店购物还是公会打造，都有可能获得强大的装备充实你的团队。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548680/extras/b843d06c7ff54ef916beb512d04f3f3f.poster.avif?t=1745568966\" width=630 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548680/extras/b843d06c7ff54ef916beb512d04f3f3f.webm?t=1745568966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548680/extras/b843d06c7ff54ef916beb512d04f3f3f.mp4?t=1745568966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>与队友交流、赠送礼物提升他们的好感。</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>通过日常工作、工会建设以及团队决策、地城探索等内容在城内站稳脚跟，<strong>但要小心，决策带来的经济压力往往会是压倒骆驼的最后一根稻草。</strong></li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>与敌人战斗，但也要与疲劳抗争。除去地城冒险，为公会付出一份力也会使自己疲惫。<strong>及时的休息可能会带来更大的收益</strong>。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548680/extras/bf1421b14fbdda16a2de5e9d8cdd3805.poster.avif?t=1745568966\" width=630 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548680/extras/bf1421b14fbdda16a2de5e9d8cdd3805.webm?t=1745568966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548680/extras/bf1421b14fbdda16a2de5e9d8cdd3805.mp4?t=1745568966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>大量随机生成的内容。<br>同伴、地城、武器装备、遭遇事件，每一次挑战都不相同。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>招募预设或随机生成的同伴角色，构建风格多变的冒险者小队</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>使用获取的珍稀素材打造独一无二的装备</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>主线通关后的完全随机生成的无限迷宫，每前进一步都是对角色养成和装备搭配的考验</li></ul>",
